an></span></span></span></div><div><span><span><span><span><span><span>            # In the “~/.bashrc” set PATH</span></span></span></span></span></span></div><div><span><span><span><span><span><span>             PATH=${PATH}:/Volumes/Data/KFH/KFH_Data/Databases/MongoDB/bin</span></span></span></span></span></span></div><div><span><span><span><span><span><span><br /></span></span></span></span></span></span></div><div><span><span><span><span><span><span><br /></span></span></span></span></span></span></div><div><span><span><span><span><span><span>Step 5: Initializing the Server.</span></span></span></span></span></span></div><div><span><span><span><span><span><span>            Create a script file and put the folllowing lines:</span></span></span></span></span></span></div><div><span><span><span><span><span>           <b> mongod </b> \</span></span></span></span></span></div><div><span><span><span><span><span>    <span>        <font color="#941100">--</font></span></span><font color="#941100">port</font> <font color="#9437ff">8102</font>  \</span></span></span></span></div><div><span><span><span><span><span><span>    <span>        <font color="#941100">--</font></span></span><font color="#941100">bind_ip_all</font> \</span></span></span></span></span></div><div><span><span><span><span><span><span>    <span>        <font color="#941100">--dbpath </font></span></span><font color="#942193"> /Volumes/Data/KFH/KFH_Data/Databases/MongoDB/db</font> \</span></span></span></span></span></div><div><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>    <span>        -<font color="#941100">-directoryperdb</font> \</span></span><br /></span></span></span></span></span></span></div><div><span><span><span><span><span><span>           <font color="#941100"> --logpath</font> <font color="#942193">/Volumes/Data/KFH/KFH_Data/Databases/MongoDB/log/</font><font color="#941751">MongoDB.log</font> \</span></span></span></span></span></span></div><div><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>            --logappend </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div><div><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>    <span>    <span>    </span></span></span><br /></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div><div><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>Step 6: Testing</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div><div><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>            =&gt; <b>mongo</b> <font color="#0433ff">--host </font><font color="#009051">127.0.0.1</font>:<font color="#9437ff">8102</font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div><div><span>    <span>       <font color="#929292"> </font></span></span><font color="#929292">MongoDB shell version v3.6.4</font></div><div><font color="#929292"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span>    <span>    <span>    </span></span></span>connecting to: mongodb://127.0.0.1:8102/</font></div></en-note>